description: Off-White’s Virgil Abloh Is the Creative Director Everyone Wants to Be | GQ
extended: A decade ago, every scrappy young kid orbiting the music industry with a heart full of hustle and a head full of rap lyrics wanted to be a CEO, like Jay Z or Diddy. Today they all want to be a creative director. Well, really they want to be Virgil Abloh.
